        <abstract> 
<p>Draws CD’s attention to a paper in <hi rend="italic">American Naturalist</hi> [3 (1869): 109] describing honey-bees killed by entanglement in pollen-masses of <hi rend="italic">Asclepias</hi>.</p> 
